data.description: This 2B/2B single family home situated on an oversized 11,000 sq.ft corner lot in Pointe West community is centrally located in West Bradenton .05 miles to Blake Hospital, medical offices, GT Bray Park, shopping and restaurants! Vinyl fence with side gate perfect for boat parking! Enter your new home to neutral ceramic tile throughout, and enjoy your spacious formal living room and dining area, the updated kitchen in 2016 has granite counters, wood cabinets, updated appliances, lazy Susan, custom lighting and fixtures, and a skylight for bright natural light. This spacious split-suite designed home features a main owners suite that has granite, and new updated tile, both suites have walk-in closets. Also includes a large enclosed and air-conditioned Florida room, new washer and dryer in 2018, and a whole house water filtration system ($8,000) PLUS BRAND new ROOF in 2022 (has the 3rd nail), Brand new WINDOWS 2022, and Hurricane garage door (2018). Homes in Pointe West are a desirable commodity and the association fees are only $35 per year and located in the highest elevation in Manatee County which means not in a flood zone! Low homeowners insurance policy just $1477 per year.
